## Description {#details}

A minidump stream represented as a sequence of hex bytes.

This is used as a fallback when no other stream kind is suitable.

Definition at line 167 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/objectyaml/minidumpyaml-h">MinidumpYAML.h</a>.
